        <mxCell id="yRlhxJY5RL-tTfC4KCpP-3" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;verticalAlign=top;labelBackgroundColor=default;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);&quot;&gt;利用 DFS 寻找包含&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;12,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;23&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Flag=0&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;边的路径。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;遇到循环点时，依次调取&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-inline&quot; data-math=&quot;D&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;17&quot; style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;中的 0、1、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-inline&quot; data-math=&quot;n&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;26&quot; style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;片段进行拼接。&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
